    <item>
      <title>收益率快速上涨后华尔街多头本周平静收官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/wall-street-bulls-end-week-unrattled-after-fast-run-up-in-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通胀担忧再度抬头、债券收益率飙升、美国总统政治局势紧张的一周之后，风险资产多头最大的收获或许是，这些因素最终并没有给他们带来多大的困扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/wall-street-bulls-end-week-unrattled-after-fast-run-up-in-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 20:24:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国债券市场的震荡周表明未来波动性将进一步加大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/whiplash-week-for-us-bonds-suggests-more-volatility-on-horizon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国债交易员们结束了动荡的一周，其中债券市场波动性指标飙升至今年新高，预示着未来还会出现更多动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/whiplash-week-for-us-bonds-suggests-more-volatility-on-horizon</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 16:01:05 GMT</pubDate>
